an the action is always just around the corner.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152530/extras/6cafe399ec9cb5c60582026c355e51ec.poster.avif?t=1771525837\" width=500 height=280 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152530/extras/6cafe399ec9cb5c60582026c355e51ec.webm?t=1771525837\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3152530/extras/6cafe399ec9cb5c60582026c355e51ec.mp4?t=1771525837\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
